following
https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ejJ-2oz4AgI

- install djangorestframework
[pip install djangorestframework]

- create an app Company
[python manage.py startapp company]

register company app to main project/seetings.py


- create model employee model in company app

- register employee model to admin

- make migration
[python manage.py makemigrations]

- migrate
[ python manage.py migrate]

- create superuser
[python manage.py createsuperuser]


- create serializer file


- create the view which will correspond to the http methods
